    <item>
      <title>英特尔确认向五角大楼提供 30 亿美元芯片资助；股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/intel-confirms-3-billion-defense-department-chips-act-grant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英特尔公司周一表示，它有资格获得高达 30 亿美元的美国政府资助，用于生产军用芯片，证实了彭博社早些时候的报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/intel-confirms-3-billion-defense-department-chips-act-grant</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 19:01:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙正在谈判赢得法国关键的欧盟委员会职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/macron-in-talks-to-win-pivotal-job-for-sejourne-at-eu-commission</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙正在与欧盟委员会进行谈判，为法国开辟一个新的、更强大的职位，他的提名人将负责监督欧盟为提升其竞争力所做的所有努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/macron-in-talks-to-win-pivotal-job-for-sejourne-at-eu-commission</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 15:44:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TikTok 因抗议美国禁令而受到法庭严厉质询</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/tiktok-appeal-of-us-ban-over-china-ties-to-be-argued-in-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从上诉法院小组的质询来看，如果中国所有者不出售这款广受欢迎的社交媒体应用，TikTok 将面临一场艰难的战斗，以避开美国的禁令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/tiktok-appeal-of-us-ban-over-china-ties-to-be-argued-in-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
